data.description: This beautiful ranch home features 3 bedrooms, 1 bath, full basement and a 2 car garage.All you have to do is literally move in. Beautiful kitchen, hardwood floors, stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, new drive way, newer roof 3 years old, water softener, beautiful landscaping, and so much more. Schedule your showing today! This won't last long!!! This home also qualifies for $7000 grant towards closing!!!
